{"tid":1027968,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【含圖】環球推四大音招《Fab Four》群P震撼樂壇！","createTime":"2019-02-19T07:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T10:40:16.000Z","uid":122522,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2461cf62e4448954768e8fdd7d30a3eaf73d97df","tid":1027968,"uid":122522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OEN190217-14832-0900-M&amp;d=1550415491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DOEN190217-14832-0900-M%26d%3D1550415491&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEv7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=f0fa0a8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OEN190217-14832-0900-M&amp;d=1550415491</a><br />\n<br />\n《Fab Four》震撼樂壇！<br />\n1/10<br />\n環球唱片於2019年全力出擊，一次過推出四組各具特色和音樂風格的新人，打造今次《Fab Four》新人企劃主題，《Fab Four》全寫是「Fabulous Four」，意思指驚人的、難以置信的四組新人單位，包括「搖滾力爆發樂隊」ONE PROMISE、有「氣質鋼琴王子」涂毓麟（Oscar Tao）、「甜美新銳女聲」陳凱詠（Jace Chan）和「新生代節奏系樂團」Dusty Bottle，環球唱片四個單位一同開啟222密碼，將於2月22日，同日全面推出新歌和MV，為樂壇帶來新景象！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">如陽光伴你系ONE PROMISE</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azhFDOK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazhFDOK.jpg&h=36e9bcc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nONE PROMISE前身為樂隊Empty，由主音文廸、結他手天衡、低音結他手Sora，以及鼓手 Anton組成，成軍十多年來首推出的創作歌《壹步》，和監製特意設計了口號式的間奏部份，他們表示：「每位成員都有一同嘅深刻感受，所以特別集合咗4個人的和聲，望能帶出志氣高昂嘅感覺」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">FF迷幻系 dusty bottle</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZATenn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZATenn.jpg&h=6bba7679&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cqWWDB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cqWWDB.jpg&h=1035496a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由鍵琴手JNY、結他手Jeff、低音結他手Matt和鼓手Kay四位大男孩，於16年成立的樂隊Dusty Bottle，今年加入女主音Kerryta，由四變五合體推出富復古味的廣東歌《You Don't Know Me》，他們表示：「希望可以作更多唔同類型嘅嘗試，唔好埋沒自己滿腦子嘅主意。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">治癒少女系 Jace Chan</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wR4kDP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwR4kDP7.jpg&h=bd1b8fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPfv03t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPfv03t.jpg&h=b455ee9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iQPxbZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iQPxbZ.jpg&h=1aedac70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳凱詠（Jace Chan）大學畢業後、參加了由環球娛樂網誌舉辦的公開選舉，由譚詠麟選出為首席主播，因精通兩文三語，曾擔任主持、司儀，拍電視節目、電影、配音、潮流拍攝等工作，機緣巧合下，唱片公司聽到她的音樂Demo，再增添「歌手」身份。她首次和與Dusty Bottle成員JNY寫歌推出處女作《想突然》，就被公司採納，她感激監製何山引導情緒，以戲劇情節投入新歌中。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">好音質鮮肉系 Oscar</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQFG7JR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQFG7JR.jpg&h=1c53c6ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1zRWca0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1zRWca0.jpg&h=960c7e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涂毓麟（Oscar Tao）是全方位音樂人，參加選秀節目《全民造星》自彈自唱後被推薦給環球唱片，踏入錄音室錄第一首歌《二人一世界》時，重覆錄唱仍未如理想，多得劉美君、郭偉亮等耐心指引及教導易掌握唱法，才順利完成作品。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他們未出道，已獲保險及鑽飾兩個大型廣告商力撐，睇好他們未來發展，其中ONE PROMISE、Jace、Kerryta＠Dusty Bottle和Oscar合作拍攝富衛保險；而Jace、Kerryta和Oscar更添食再拍MaBelle鑽飾廣告。"},{"pid":"d8143b9842f9210401328338a158a9849563554f","tid":1027968,"uid":122522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae6f341b3414d032be35927bc757a31b025ff55","tid":1027968,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:28:50.000Z","msg":"Fab Fab Fab Fab"},{"pid":"e1be3e055b35525a23e7087303d4bdede0fc28b4","tid":1027968,"uid":194986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:49:18.000Z","msg":"公子Oscar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278169919fb27e87ef9a44e436e537b1c0a53428","tid":1027968,"uid":23400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"Fab乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51d26fd6b6f4b5f7cccf52dd4ee6ffbd4f9bc26","tid":1027968,"uid":72195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"印象中，全民造星有幾個仲唱得好過Oscar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a8997f9548d7230b084a7cd591dc4f143332ad","tid":1027968,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:57:03.000Z","msg":"Dusty Bottle正嘢"},{"pid":"6e0e285405f3c9c66c292edb51dbbd37c47bd148","tid":1027968,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"Jace Chan 幾正"}]}